        <mxCell id="current_body" value="• Tauri 透明桌宠窗口&lt;br&gt;• 低打扰 CatStateMachine&lt;br&gt;• localhost HTTP API&lt;br&gt;• PetEvent JSON Schema / whitelist / token&lt;br&gt;• diagnostics / ingress queue&lt;br&gt;• petctl notify&lt;br&gt;• safe sound feedback&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;可声明：macOS-first MVP ready" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F8FAFC;strokeColor=#64748B;align=left;spacingLeft=16;fontSize=14" vertex="1" parent="1">
